    m_VerticalOverflow: 0
    m_LineSpacing: 1
  m_Text: 'Rodent Problem Prototype Information


    Controls:

    Move - W/A/S/D

    Dash
    - Shift (Two per cooldown cycle)

    Melee - F (Press for quick attack, hold
    for big attack)

    Shoot - Left Mouse

    Reload - R

    Weapon Select -
    1 for fully automatic rifle (brown), 2 for semi automatic pistol (grey)

    Interact
    - E (to purchase doors)

    Menu - Escape


    Check out the notes section
    for more info'
